## ğŸ§  Why I Built This
As someone with ADHD, I constantly struggled with:
- Forgetting medications ("Did I take my pills today?")
- Missing appointments (time blindness)
- Last-minute panic when arriving places
- "Out of sight, out of mind" tasks

This app solves those problems with **brain-friendly reminders**.

## âœ¨ Key Features
| Feature | How It Helps ADHD |
|---------|-------------------|
| ğŸ”Š **Voice Alerts** | Auditory cues bypass working memory issues |
| ğŸ“ **Location Triggers** | "Buy milk when near grocery store" reminders |
| ğŸ•’ **Time-Based** | Visual countdowns for time blindness |
| ğŸ†˜ **Emergency Mode** | One-tap location sharing with caregivers |

